---
title: Haloumi, Bacon & Avocado Cos Salad with Jammy Eggs, Mustard Dressing & Almonds
description: Don’t worry this is nothing like your garden variety salad - this one has flavour popping like fireworks. Salty and
squeaky haloumi next to bacon and a soft boiled egg all wrapped up in a cos lettuce salad sure sounds like an exciting
take on a salad - but we’ll let you try it for yourself.
